{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273750/extras/addtowishlist_gif.gif?t=1734929781\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Combine. Split. Promote.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Chessplus unlocks exponentially more moves and new strategies in this Chess variant by allowing players to <strong>combine and split</strong> <strong>pieces</strong>, enabling two pieces to move together while utilizing the abilities of both.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273750/extras/chessplus_pieces.gif?t=1734929781\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Battle the AI in <strong>Singleplayer</strong> mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Challenge the world in seamless cross-platform <strong>Online Multiplayer</strong>\u00a0and <strong>Local Multiplayer</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dive into a relentless <strong>Roguelike</strong> <strong>Adventure</strong> mode, where every choice matters</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>How to Play</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Use traditional Chess moves to combine your pieces.</strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273750/extras/combine_65pc.gif?t=1734929781\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Combined pieces can move as either piece.</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273750/extras/combine2_65pc.gif?t=1734929781\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Unlock new strategies by splitting your pieces into their original forms</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamst